则特征向量$\vec u_{i}^\star$对应的$\vec y_i^\star$

$$
\vec y_i^\star = c_i e_i \quad e_i\text{为单位向量}
$$


考虑

$$
\begin{align*}
R &amp;= \frac{\sum \lambda_i y_i^2}{\sum y_i^2}
\end{align*}
$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
\frac{\partial R}{\partial y_i} &amp;= \frac{2 \lambda_i y_i \left( \sum y_j^2 \right) - \left( \sum \lambda_j y_j^2 \right) 2 y_i}{\left( \sum y_j^2 \right)^2} \\
&amp;= \frac{2 y_i \sum_{j \neq i} (\lambda_i - \lambda_j) y_j^2}{\left( \sum y_j^2 \right)^2}
\end{align*}
$$

容易发现, $y_i = 0$或$\vec y = \vec y_i^\star$是其零点

所以

$$\frac{\partial R}{\partial y_k} \bigg|_{\vec y = \vec y_i^\star} = 0, k = 1, \dots, n$$

div.data-content:
取$u = Uy$

其中

$$
\begin{cases}
U^T K U &= \Lambda \\
U^T M U &= I
\end{cases}
$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
R &= \frac{y^T U^T K U y}{y^T U^T M U y} \\
&= \frac{y^T \Lambda y}{y^T y} \\
&= \frac{\sum \lambda_i y_i^2}{\sum y_i^2}
\end{align*}
$$

容易知

$$\lambda_1 \leq R(u) \leq \lambda_n$$

div.style: display: flex; align-items: unsafe center; justify-content: unsafe flex-start; width: 1px; height: 1px; padding-top: 900px; margin-left: 72px;
display: inline-block; font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 1.2; pointer-events: all; white-space: nowrap;

div.data-content:
取$u = Uy$


则特征向量$\vec u_{i}^\star$对应的$\vec y_i^\star$

$$
\vec y_i^\star = c_i e_i \quad e_i\text{为单位向量}
$$


考虑

$$
\begin{align*}
R &= \frac{\sum \lambda_i y_i^2}{\sum y_i^2}
\end{align*}
$$

则

$$
\begin{align*}
\frac{\partial R}{\partial y_i} &= \frac{2 \lambda_i y_i \left( \sum y_j^2 \right) - \left( \sum \lambda_j y_j^2 \right) 2 y_i}{\left( \sum y_j^2 \right)^2} \\
&= \frac{2 y_i \sum_{j \neq i} (\lambda_i - \lambda_j) y_j^2}{\left( \sum y_j^2 \right)^2}
\end{align*}
$$

容易发现, $y_i = 0$或$\vec y = \vec y_i^\star$是其零点

所以

$$\frac{\partial R}{\partial y_k} \bigg|_{\vec y = \vec y_i^\star} = 0, k = 1, \dots, n$$

$$\nabla R(u) = \frac{2}{(u^T M u)^2} \left[ (u^T M u) K u - (u^T K u) M u \right]$$

由$K u_i = \lambda_i M u_i$

$$\nabla R(u_i) = \frac{2}{(u_i^T M u_i)^2} \left[ (u_i^T M u_i) \lambda_i M u_i - (\lambda_i u_i^T M u_i) M u_i \right] = 0$$

说明$\lambda_i = R(u_i)$为驻值
